text: The U.S. Bank Building is a low-rise U.S. Bancorp office building located in Sioux Falls, South Dakota. At 128.93 feet, it is the 7th tallest building in Sioux Falls, and the 9th tallest in the state of South Dakota. ==References== Category:Buildings and structures in Sioux Falls, South Dakota Category:Office buildings in South Dakota
title: U.S. Bank Building (Sioux Falls)
